 none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000000; b=
order-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">a 2011 paper</a> by Sus=
an Lorde Martin on =E2=80=9CBetting on the Lives of Strangers: Life Settlem=
ents, STOLI, and Securitization,=E2=80=9D making this point:</p><blockquote=
><p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The life insurance industry argues that its s=
urrender value schedule<a class=3D"footnote-index" href=3D"#footnote-8" sty=
le=3D"color: #000000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width=
