000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">10 years</a>, =
meaning that there are a lot of suboptimal prepayments.</p><p style=3D"marg=
in: 16px 0;">If you could move without prepaying your mortgage =E2=80=94=C2=
=A0if you could just transfer your mortgage to whoever is buying your house=
 =E2=80=94=C2=A0then you would, and all cheap mortgages would remain outsta=
nding for 30 years, and=C2=A0the whole mortgage market would be mispriced. =
